api_list.name: countries_geocoders
api_list.description:
Return a list of available geocoders.
As defined in settings.GEOCODING_SERVICE_SETTINGS
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://geophysics.p.rapidapi.com/countries/geocoders/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "geophysics.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
